To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

> Copies of any NASA work contracts awarded to consultancy ICF as of the date the search is conducted. Please limit your search to contracts that were active beginning on or after January 1, 2020.

> Copies of any research reports, white papers, presentations, or other text-based deliverables consultancy ICF produced as a result of NASA work contracts that were active between January 1, 2020, and the date the search is conducted.

>  Copies of any statements, disclosure forms, or other documents related to disclosing organizational or personal conflicts of interest that consultancy ICF submitted in association with contracts awarded by NASA as of the date the search is conducted. Please limit your search to contracts that were active beginning on or after January 1, 2020.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Madeleine Stone
